targets.name: key
targets.tooltip: Full path to file, including bucket name. This is the value returned in 'Upload File''s key output.

targets.name: bucket
targets.tooltip: Using 'key' often require knowing current user' ID. If you don't have this value, you can use 'bucket' + 'path' and the server will automatically insert user ID into the path.

targets.name: path
targets.tooltip: Using 'key' often require knowing current user' ID. If you don't have this value, you can use 'bucket' + 'path' and the server will automatically insert user ID into the path.
